\pard\cf1\f0\fs24 I don't like to watch Horror movies because I can't sleep in the night after watching that kind of movies.\par
Since I can learn true events from it, I like to watch documentary movies.\par
I watched a comedy movie. I almost fell off my chair.\par
It takes a great deal of skill to make such funny movies without sound, without technical equipment, as Charli did.\par
Once, watching a sci-fi movie I thought that it must be exciting to discover other solar system.\par
}
